006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.datatype.markup.flexmark;
007
008import com.vladsch.flexmark.util.ast.Document;
009
010import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
011import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.SuppressFBWarnings;
012
013@SuppressFBWarnings("THROWS_METHOD_THROWS_CLAUSE_THROWABLE")
014public interface IMarkupVisitor<T, E extends Throwable> {
015  /**
016   * A visitor callback used to visit a markdown syntax tree.
017   *
018   * @param document
019   *          the markdown syntax tree
020   * @param writer
021   *          a markup writer used to generate markup output
022   * @throws E
023   *           the visitor exception Java type
024   */
025  void visitDocument(@NonNull Document document, @NonNull IMarkupWriter<T, E> writer) throws E;
026}
